      "message": "Can you clarify if they are scheduled if the build action is scheduled, but don\u0027t have to complete before the build action, or before any dependents of the build action can be started?\n\nIf they are scheduled at any point in the build, but don\u0027t block the dependents of the build action, how are they handled in an interrupted and restarted build if `my_program` has been completed, but `my_program_style_check` has not?",
